sss","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Almost all the tech companies are doing from last one year","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:45 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Cause of recession and everything","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"Ohhhh","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"That’s not good","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:46 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Yess..right","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:47 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"How was your day ma'am","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"What did you do","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I slept and talked to u","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:48 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"Okkay","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:49 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"How was your day sir","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:50 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"It was somewhat okay today..not much work","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:50 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I missed you tho","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:51 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"},{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I did too","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:52 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"I was feeling sleepy so much","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:52 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But as my eyes opened I looked for my phone","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:53 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","text":"But then I end up sleeping again 🙂","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:53 am","kind":"msg"},{"sender":"Aamir | عامر","text":"I thought you were sleeping.. I wanted you to rest","time":"Feb 02, 2024 10:54 am","kind":"msg","reactions":[{"reactor":"Bushra Khan","emoji":"❤️"}]},{"sender":"Bushra Khan","